<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ النازعات<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{يَوْمَ تَرْجُفُ الرَّاجِفَةُ , تَتْبَعُهَا الرَّادِفَةُ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٨ص١٠٨:</span> <span class="c3">{الرَّاجِفَةُ}</span>: النَّفْخَةُ الأُولَى.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَ <span class="c3">{الرَّادِفَةُ}</span>: النَّفْخَةُ الثَّانِيَةُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [النازعات: ٦، ٧]</p> </div>